        "description" : " Returns an approximation to the mathematical constant .This function is deterministic, context-independent,  and focus-independent. This function returns the xs:double value whose lexical representation is\n             3.141592653589793e0The expression 2*math:pi() returns 6.283185307179586e0.The expression 60 * (math:pi() div 180) converts an angle of 60 degrees\n                to radians. \n", 
        "params" : [  ]
